cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper proposes a new family of neural models that combine the benefits of deep neural networks and Bayesian methods such as Gaussian Processes. The paper focuses on machine learning tasks such as regression, classification, and image completion. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) tasks, which are closely related to machine learning. Additionally, the paper introduces a new approach that combines neural networks and stochastic processes, which falls under the category of neural engineering (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
